    <item>
      <title>空客季度盈利因航天部门收费而下滑</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-30/airbus-tktktkt-on-slower-plane-deliveries</link>
      <description><![CDATA[空中客车集团第二季度的营业利润下降了一半以上，原因是该公司在其航天部门登记了一笔费用，迫使其在飞机交付量低于预期的情况下削减成本。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-30/airbus-tktktkt-on-slower-plane-deliveries</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 30 Jul 2024 15:52:53 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>监狱电话公司 ViaPath 在新的 FCC 规则下完成 13.8 亿美元债务出售</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-30/prison-phone-company-viapath-wraps-up-1-4-billion-debt-sale-after-new-fcc-rules</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于美国联邦通信委员会出台新规定限制监狱通信提供商 ViaPath Technologies 的通话收费标准，该公司暂停了该流程，目前已完成 13.8 亿美元的再融资交易。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-30/prison-phone-company-viapath-wraps-up-1-4-billion-debt-sale-after-new-fcc-rules</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 30 Jul 2024 15:49:37 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>穆迪将英国南部水务公司的评级下调至垃圾级</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-30/uk-s-southern-water-risks-downgrade-to-junk-by-moody-s</link>
      <description><![CDATA[穆迪评级正在考虑将英国公用事业公司南方水务公司的优先债务评级下调至垃圾级，这一最新迹象表明，泰晤士水务公司的困境可能蔓延至英国水务行业的其他领域。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-30/uk-s-southern-water-risks-downgrade-to-junk-by-moody-s</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 30 Jul 2024 15:35:54 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>阿拉比卡咖啡价格因供应担忧缓解而维持近三周低点</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-30/arabica-coffee-holds-near-three-week-low-on-easing-supply-fears</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于交易商评估了主要种植区巴西冬季的温和天气条件以及需求疲软的风险，阿拉比卡咖啡期货交易价格接近三周来的最低水平。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-30/arabica-coffee-holds-near-three-week-low-on-easing-supply-fears</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 30 Jul 2024 12:22:19 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
